* Iron Raptor looked to the Ark and a sigh escaped her lips, they had gotten 
inside! The Predacons were tricky bots to try and tackle but then again, the 
Maximals weren't so easily defeated. They stood proud and true no matter the 
cost, or so it seemed to her at the time.
Iron Raptor put her sword away and looked around at the sceen, there weren't 
that many Preds out in the open but that also meant that they were mostly in 
the base! Not a good thing!
She sighed again as she looked over the shield that now covered the base, 
obviously Iris was sustaining it but her power supply could only last so 
long...then what?
Iron Raptor growled as she made her way back towards the Ark, her splatter 
gun in hand. It was then that she spotted a new bot, and then another!
She snarled, another raptor and a fuzor...but at least they were on their 
side.
Iron Raptor saw that the fuzor was closest and opened her com-link to it...*

" Attention, bot 663(Teltoli). Please specify your name and function."

* She looked up at the fuzor and snarled again, she knew that it was going 
out on a limb but she had to find out who and what it was.
Allies are very important to a group that was outnumbered.*
